caption.text:
The DRE Dream Tour to Spiti Valley was not just a ride. It was a dream that was lived by Ducatisti who chose to take their Ducati to some of the most treacherous terrains in India and came back as better riders and friends. During the 7 day expedition, they crossed small villages, river crossings, roads, no roads, met new people and made memories that will last a lifetime. Here's a small glimpse from the ride and stay tuned for more content! 
It was an unforgettable experience and we can't wait to go back.

Ride partners: @shell and @pirelli
Ride curator: @eagleriderindia
